    {
      "name": "AI Assistant",
      "description": "Natural-language query endpoint. Backend forwards the question to Gemini with a tool spec, executes the chosen tool against MongoDB, then asks Gemini to format a response.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Ask",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ai/ask",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "ai", "ask"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"question\": \"Who came in late today?\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Manager/admin only.\n\n**Available tools** (Gemini picks one based on the question):\n- `get_late_arrivals(date?, threshold_hour?)`\n- `get_employees_under_8hrs(date?)`\n- `get_pending_overtime()`\n- `get_attendance_summary(start_date?, end_date?)`\n- `get_user_history(name, limit?)`\n- `get_disabled_users()`\n\n**Returns** `{ answer, tool_used, tool_args, tool_result }` so the frontend can show what the agent did.\n\n**Try these questions**\n- \"Who came in late today?\"\n- \"Show me employees with under 8 hours yesterday\"\n- \"Any pending overtime requests?\"\n- \"Give me a summary for this week\"\n- \"Show Aman's last 5 records\"\n- \"Which users are disabled?\""
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK — late arrivals",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"answer\": \"Two employees punched in after 9 AM today: Riya Sharma at 09:42 and Aman Verma at 10:15.\",\n  \"tool_used\": \"get_late_arrivals\",\n  \"tool_args\": { \"date\": \"2026-05-05\", \"threshold_hour\": 9 },\n  \"tool_result\": [\n    { \"name\": \"Riya Sharma\", \"email\": \"riya@sentry.dev\", \"punch_in\": \"09:42\", \"date\": \"2026-05-05\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Aman Verma\", \"email\": \"aman@sentry.dev\", \"punch_in\": \"10:15\", \"date\": \"2026-05-05\" }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "200 OK — summary",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"answer\": \"This week (May 1–5): 23 records, 18 present, 4 incomplete, 1 OT pending. Total 184.5 hours worked.\",\n  \"tool_used\": \"get_attendance_summary\",\n  \"tool_args\": { \"start_date\": \"2026-05-01\", \"end_date\": \"2026-05-05\" },\n  \"tool_result\": {\n    \"range\": \"2026-05-01 to 2026-05-05\",\n    \"total_records\": 23,\n    \"present\": 18,\n    \"incomplete\": 4,\n    \"ot_pending\": 1,\n    \"total_hours\": 184.5\n  }\n}"
            }
